02:02.020 --> 02:02.989
Okay, smile.

02:03.022 --> 02:04.123
Come on.
Let's just go.

02:04.156 --> 02:04.990
I'm sick of taking a pictures.

02:05.023 --> 02:05.624
One more time.

02:05.657 --> 02:07.025
Do you want a picture.

02:07.058 --> 02:07.861
Wait.

02:07.893 --> 02:09.061
Batteries are dead.

02:09.095 --> 02:10.130
No, I just replaced them.

02:18.404 --> 02:21.007
-Excuse me.
-Yeah.

02:21.040 --> 02:22.108
No, it can't be.

02:22.141 --> 02:23.977
You... you seem way to young.

02:24.010 --> 02:27.647
-You look identical to someone...
-Look, I gotta go.

02:27.679 --> 02:30.883
-Sorry.
-Sure, yeah, sorry.

03:29.475 --> 03:31.945
Yes, we talked about this two
weeks ago. No,

03:31.977 --> 03:33.278
I need an answer
quicker than that.

03:33.311 --> 03:35.047
Hold on.
Hello.

03:35.081 --> 03:36.082
I got to call you back.

03:39.218 --> 03:43.655
I don't care... I don't care
what the Bishop thinks.

03:43.689 --> 03:46.091
Look, father, I'll raise the
money myself in I have to.

03:46.125 --> 03:50.196
I'll rob a bank if necessary.

03:50.228 --> 03:53.499
No, I won't rob a bank.
Joe, wait.

03:53.531 --> 03:55.000
Come here.

03:55.034 --> 03:56.335
What baby?

03:56.369 --> 03:58.137
Those kids are dying
of hunger, father.

03:58.169 --> 04:00.639
They can't wait
for your meeting.

04:00.673 --> 04:01.607
Is this all we've got?

04:01.639 --> 04:02.642
No, we got more.

04:02.674 --> 04:04.076
But not what you wanted.

04:04.109 --> 04:05.978
No, I'm right here.

04:06.012 --> 04:06.513
What point?

04:06.546 --> 04:08.180
What are you doing.

04:08.214 --> 04:10.149
I don't care what
religion those people are.

04:10.181 --> 04:10.683
Those kids are
dying of hunger.

04:10.715 --> 04:11.451
They need food.

04:11.483 --> 04:13.151
Not a cross.

04:13.185 --> 04:15.121
No, no, the point is
we need to help them.

04:15.154 --> 04:16.456
That's the point.

04:16.488 --> 04:17.488
Ok, look.

04:18.224 --> 04:19.558
Have your meeting.

04:19.591 --> 04:21.461
Analyze whatever
you need to analyze.

04:21.493 --> 04:22.294
I'm going forward with
or without your blessing.

04:26.065 --> 04:27.267
We need more shoes.

04:51.089 --> 04:52.257
Hello.

04:52.291 --> 04:54.026
Yeah.

04:54.060 --> 04:55.060
So how much they need?

04:57.829 --> 04:59.298
That's some kind of dough.

06:10.469 --> 06:11.771
Hi, grandpa.

06:11.803 --> 06:12.671
Hi Emmett.

06:12.704 --> 06:14.173
Sorry, I'm late.

06:14.205 --> 06:15.507
-Hello, Dave.
-Hey, pops.

06:15.541 --> 06:16.409
Hey, I got a great
weekend planned.

06:16.442 --> 06:17.043
Ok.

06:17.075 --> 06:18.111
I'll take us to the game.

06:18.144 --> 06:19.278
Ok.

06:19.310 --> 06:20.479
And whatever else
you want to do.

06:20.512 --> 06:22.114
Ok, we'll go to
the batting cages.

06:22.147 --> 06:22.681
Sounds like fun.

06:22.714 --> 06:23.381
Grab your stuff.

06:23.414 --> 06:24.616
Let's go.

06:24.649 --> 06:25.550
Do want to here on Sunday?

06:25.584 --> 06:27.120
-I'll call you.
-Ok.

06:27.152 --> 06:27.819
Have a good weekend, Emmett.

06:27.853 --> 06:28.588
Ok, bye, Dad.

06:28.620 --> 06:29.621
See you.

07:14.332 --> 07:15.400
You looking for me?

07:15.433 --> 07:17.435
Yeah.

07:17.469 --> 07:21.873
I'm sorry... I didn't mean
to... I mean... how you doing?

07:21.906 --> 07:23.476
My name's Jimmy Anderson.

07:23.509 --> 07:26.246
-there's something
I'd like to show you.

07:46.397 --> 07:48.333
Reporter took these photos.

07:48.366 --> 07:52.437
And... that man
saved my life in Vietnam.

07:54.240 --> 07:56.942
But I never found
out who he was.

07:56.976 --> 07:58.911
I mean, he just came out of
the blue and then he just left.

07:59.812 --> 08:01.913
I never saw him again.

08:01.947 --> 08:03.349
He looks identical to you.

08:05.284 --> 08:09.255
-except that he should
be like 40 something now.

08:09.288 --> 08:10.590
I mean, the
resemblance is amazing.

08:10.623 --> 08:11.990
That's what puzzled.

08:12.024 --> 08:14.293
I'm thinking maybe
this is someone

08:14.325 --> 08:16.361
who could have been
related to you?

08:16.394 --> 08:17.897
Why do you want
to find this man?

08:18.663 --> 08:20.265
Why?

08:20.298 --> 08:21.834
Yes.

08:21.866 --> 08:24.736
To find out what his name is.

08:24.769 --> 08:25.471
To thank him.

08:26.538 --> 08:29.475
Buy him a beer.

08:29.507 --> 08:31.276
Well, even if you
never find him,

08:31.310 --> 08:33.546
I'm sure the thought counts.

08:33.578 --> 08:34.647
I got to go.

08:34.679 --> 08:36.280
Sorry.

08:36.315 --> 08:37.650
Look, this is the
closest I've ever gotten

08:37.682 --> 08:40.318
to really finding this man.

08:40.352 --> 08:41.453
I can't help you right now.

08:41.486 --> 08:43.356
Well, that's ok.

08:43.388 --> 08:45.358
I mean, we can meet
tomorrow or some other time.

08:45.391 --> 08:47.325
I just want to pick your brain.

08:47.358 --> 08:48.661
Maybe we can put two
and two together.

08:51.296 --> 08:53.233
I think you're looking
in the wrong places.

08:54.833 --> 08:56.236
What do you mean?

08:57.735 --> 09:00.372
Is the man in the pictures
what you're really looking for?

09:00.406 --> 09:01.774
Of course.

09:01.806 --> 09:02.841
Who else?

09:02.874 --> 09:04.042
I don't know.

09:04.075 --> 09:04.911
That's why I'm asking.

09:08.881 --> 09:10.683
Look, I'm sorry.

09:10.715 --> 09:12.618
I really have to go.

09:12.651 --> 09:14.954
Look, I'd really to have a
talk with you some other time.

09:14.987 --> 09:16.856
Some other time.

09:16.888 --> 09:18.657
Where can I find you?

09:18.690 --> 09:19.791
Around here.

09:19.825 --> 09:21.694
Just ask for me.

09:21.727 --> 09:23.429
Well, what's your name?

10:29.762 --> 10:31.796
Hey, Joe.

10:31.829 --> 10:35.368
Father, I'm going
to go home now.

10:35.401 --> 10:36.635
There are still some people
over there in the church.

10:36.667 --> 10:38.503
So I didn't lock it.

10:38.536 --> 10:40.506
Anything else you
need before I go?

10:40.539 --> 10:41.507
No thanks.

10:41.540 --> 10:42.541
Ok.

10:42.574 --> 10:43.709
Good night.

10:43.742 --> 10:44.743
Good night.

10:49.714 --> 10:50.983
Why did you hide?

10:51.983 --> 10:53.118
I don't know.

10:54.853 --> 10:55.854
It was a reaction.

11:18.142 --> 11:18.911
Catherine, look at me.

11:24.583 --> 11:25.385
No.

11:26.785 --> 11:27.286
No what?

11:29.921 --> 11:30.922
What you're thinking.

11:33.224 --> 11:34.026
What I'm thinking.

11:40.065 --> 11:41.133
You have a husband,
and I have a church.

11:57.950 --> 11:59.185
It's your husband.

11:59.218 --> 12:00.520
What is he doing here?

12:01.719 --> 12:02.954
I do want to see him.

12:03.988 --> 12:05.023
But I have to answer the door.

12:06.190 --> 12:07.593
I can't see right now.

12:07.626 --> 12:08.161
I just can't.

12:22.007 --> 12:23.943
May I help you?

12:23.975 --> 12:25.710
Father Michael,
I guess you remember me.

12:25.743 --> 12:27.213
I'm Catherine's husband.

12:28.113 --> 12:29.915
Yes, of course.

12:29.948 --> 12:30.950
I'll never forget
anybody I marry.

12:34.652 --> 12:35.620
I'd like to have
a talk with you.

12:39.657 --> 12:40.892
I'm in the middle of
something right now.

12:40.925 --> 12:41.927
Can you come back tomorrow?

12:44.629 --> 12:45.930
Tomorrow's going
to be difficult.

12:45.964 --> 12:46.898
I only need a few minutes.

12:52.704 --> 12:53.506
Ok.

12:53.872 --> 12:55.141
Come in.

12:56.842 --> 12:58.044
Thanks.

12:59.744 --> 13:01.147
I normally don't smoke.

13:03.114 --> 13:05.517
You're probably surprised
to see me, father.

13:09.086 --> 13:12.257
I think my wife
is seeing someone.

13:14.126 --> 13:15.761
What makes you think that?

13:15.794 --> 13:18.631
I... I can't pinpoint it.

13:18.664 --> 13:20.900
I don't
have any proof.

13:20.932 --> 13:21.600
It's a gut feeling.

13:25.570 --> 13:27.606
I hardly ever see her
anymore.

13:29.741 --> 13:31.577
Well, you can't just
go on gut feeling alone.

13:33.011 --> 13:34.213
You can tell those things.

13:34.246 --> 13:37.683
The way she dresses.

13:37.715 --> 13:40.084
It's the way she looks at me.

13:40.118 --> 13:42.555
It's not one specific thing.

13:42.588 --> 13:45.625
It's just a combination
of a lot of little things.

13:49.695 --> 13:52.263
I try talking to her.

13:52.296 --> 13:54.332
How do you talk
about these things.

13:54.366 --> 13:55.234
It's difficult.

14:03.275 --> 14:05.411
So how can I help you?

14:09.281 --> 14:11.215
I figured if she were
to have told anyone,

14:11.248 --> 14:13.552
she would have told
you during confession.

14:15.186 --> 14:16.821
Confessions are confidential.

14:16.854 --> 14:18.856
You know, I was

14:18.890 --> 14:20.693
hoping you could help me out.

14:20.725 --> 14:22.293
Maybe you noticed something
or she said something.

14:22.326 --> 14:24.563
I mean, we've got a kid.

14:26.263 --> 14:29.000
I'm just trying to
keep it together.

14:31.670 --> 14:33.072
My god.

14:33.104 --> 14:34.138
What's going on here?

14:34.171 --> 14:34.906
It's not what you think.

14:34.940 --> 14:36.308
I swear.

14:36.340 --> 14:37.942
No, no, no,
we'll just all sit down.

14:37.975 --> 14:38.643
We'll work...

14:38.676 --> 14:39.777
You son of...

14:39.810 --> 14:40.278
No.

14:41.680 --> 14:42.714
Father.

14:44.815 --> 14:46.051
Father, I'm so sorry.

14:53.724 --> 14:54.926
No, don't shoot.

14:54.959 --> 14:55.961
Shut up!

15:05.103 --> 15:05.905
Daddy, no.

15:07.805 --> 15:10.343
Just give me the gun,
nothing happened between us.

15:11.142 --> 15:12.677
Just give me your gun.

15:15.946 --> 15:17.682
How could you do this?

15:35.032 --> 15:36.034
Happy birthday.

17:56.007 --> 17:57.575
Hello, may I help you?

17:57.609 --> 17:59.411
Yeah, I need a room.

17:59.443 --> 18:00.845
For how many night?

18:02.113 --> 18:02.914
I don't know.

18:27.939 --> 18:30.275
It's a tall guy, blond hair.

18:30.307 --> 18:32.109
He told me I could
find him here.

18:32.142 --> 18:34.046
I have a picture right here.

18:35.580 --> 18:37.383
That's the man I'm looking
for.

18:38.650 --> 18:39.852
Look I don't think I know
him.

18:39.884 --> 18:40.652
Ok?

18:40.686 --> 18:44.156
He was here a
couple nights ago.

18:44.189 --> 18:45.623
Look Father Michael
might know him.

18:45.657 --> 18:46.959
But he's saying mass right
now.

18:46.991 --> 18:48.026
I don't know him.

18:48.058 --> 18:49.360
Yeah, I think he must.

18:50.996 --> 18:52.430
Let me give you my address.

18:52.463 --> 18:53.331
Just ask the priest
to give it to him, ok?

18:59.036 --> 19:00.038
Thanks.

19:10.382 --> 19:12.383
last night if you
saw bright lights,

19:12.417 --> 19:14.920
unusual colors, and
odd shapes flying

19:14.952 --> 19:17.455
over the Phoenix sky,
you weren't the only one.

19:17.488 --> 19:18.457
Now what that something
was is in question.

20:46.745 --> 20:48.313
Yes?

20:48.345 --> 20:50.414
Sorry, to bother you, Father.

20:50.448 --> 20:53.451
But they've been trying to
get you from the office.

20:53.485 --> 20:56.154
Your phone seems
to be off the hook.

20:56.187 --> 20:58.490
What time is it?

20:58.523 --> 20:59.391
It's 2 in the afternoon.

21:07.097 --> 21:08.099
That looks good.

21:14.706 --> 21:17.109
I'll tell you, everything that
I've seen so far looks great.

21:17.142 --> 21:19.111
I'm going through your chart.

21:19.143 --> 21:20.045
I've looked at your labs.

21:20.077 --> 21:22.613
I've looked at your x-rays.

21:22.646 --> 21:24.482
All your results turned
out to be normal.

21:24.516 --> 21:26.450
Physically I think
you're in great shape.

21:26.484 --> 21:28.353
But this time I think we need
to take it a step further

21:28.385 --> 21:31.355
and get a psychological
evaluation.

21:31.389 --> 21:32.623
What are you suggesting?

21:32.657 --> 21:33.358
Is something mental...

21:33.391 --> 21:34.659
No, I'm not saying it's mental.

21:34.691 --> 21:36.428
What I'm saying at
this point we need

21:36.460 --> 21:39.296
to have you see a
psychiatrist to evaluate

21:39.330 --> 21:40.499
the other aspects so I can
put all this stuff together.

22:40.458 --> 22:43.161
I saw a
dream, which made me afraid.

22:44.661 --> 22:47.699
And the thoughts upon my bed
and the visions of my head

22:47.731 --> 22:48.733
trouble me.

22:49.534 --> 22:52.438
Visions of my head trouble
me.

22:54.205 --> 22:55.340
Visions of my head trouble
me.

22:57.741 --> 22:59.110
Daniel 4:5.

23:00.577 --> 23:03.114
Daniel 4:5.

23:03.148 --> 23:04.283
4, 5, 4, 5.

23:08.286 --> 23:09.188
Daniel, Daniel, Daniel.

23:17.161 --> 23:20.565
I saw a dream, which
made me afraid.

23:20.597 --> 23:23.434
And the thoughts upon my bed and
the visions of my head trouble me.

23:24.536 --> 23:25.536
Daniel.

23:49.259 --> 23:50.295
Hi.

23:52.529 --> 23:54.365
I think someone was
looking for you.

23:56.200 --> 23:57.169
He showed me some pictures.

23:57.201 --> 23:59.203
And I think it's you.

24:01.639 --> 24:03.275
Anyway, he told me to
give you this address.

24:04.441 --> 24:05.443
Ok.

24:12.350 --> 24:13.485
He didn't have blue eyes.

24:55.392 --> 24:56.260
Why are you crying?

24:57.795 --> 25:00.399
Because I don't like math.

25:02.499 --> 25:04.202
Math.

25:06.504 --> 25:07.472
I'll tell you a secret.

25:09.373 --> 25:10.942
I have a PhD in chemistry, and
I still count on my fingers.

25:12.376 --> 25:13.945
But I don't want to be a PhD.

25:15.880 --> 25:16.815
What do you want to be?

25:16.847 --> 25:17.515
A chef.

25:18.882 --> 25:19.617
I see.

25:20.884 --> 25:22.386
Why aren't you at work?

25:22.420 --> 25:23.322
My daddy's at work right now.

25:27.592 --> 25:32.264
Well, about a year ago on
a very beautiful spring day

25:32.296 --> 25:34.598
I was going to work just
like every other day.

25:34.632 --> 25:38.737
And I thought what
if I just kept going.

25:38.769 --> 25:40.537
So I took off my tie.

25:40.571 --> 25:43.475
And I just drove
and drove and drove.

25:44.808 --> 25:46.677
Did your boss get mad at you?

25:46.710 --> 25:47.178
No.

25:48.313 --> 25:49.480
Well, a little bit.

25:51.415 --> 25:53.517
George, it's me,
Jimmy.

25:54.919 --> 25:57.389
I'm far, real far.

25:59.324 --> 26:02.260
Well, but I quit.

26:04.094 --> 26:05.596
No, I'm not kidding.

26:06.863 --> 26:08.365
What family?

26:08.399 --> 26:09.267
I have no family.

26:10.468 --> 26:12.469
Actually you gave me an idea.

26:12.503 --> 26:14.472
I should start one now that
I'm divorcing the company.

26:14.505 --> 26:15.507
Crazy?

26:17.441 --> 26:18.942
Well, you know,
sometimes you just

26:18.976 --> 26:20.312
have to do what
you really want.

26:22.046 --> 26:23.282
So long, George.

26:32.523 --> 26:35.427
My daddy doesn't like his
boss.

26:35.459 --> 26:36.961
Maybe I should tell him
to do the same thing.

26:38.696 --> 26:39.698
Come on, let's go.

27:46.497 --> 27:48.400
Father
Daniel, good to see you.

27:48.432 --> 27:49.600
Long way, Michael.

27:49.633 --> 27:50.735
You made it.

27:50.767 --> 27:51.736
It
was a good drive.

27:51.768 --> 27:52.871
It was good.

27:52.903 --> 27:55.038
Just a little hard to find.

27:55.072 --> 27:57.941
Finding
me can be difficult.

27:57.975 --> 27:58.910
I'm happy you're here,
Michael.

28:05.115 --> 28:06.117
Have a seat.

28:09.620 --> 28:11.656
Father, the
reason I came here today

28:11.689 --> 28:13.458
is because I want
to talk to you...

28:13.490 --> 28:14.992
I haven't
been a priest for what?

28:15.026 --> 28:16.527
10 years.

28:16.561 --> 28:18.530
You don't need to
call me father.

28:18.563 --> 28:23.001
Well, a priest is
always a priest.

28:23.034 --> 28:25.536
You sounded preoccupied
on the phone.

28:26.903 --> 28:27.905
What's going on?

28:31.776 --> 28:34.612
About a year ago or so I
started to get these headaches.

28:34.644 --> 28:37.014
At the beginning I
thought it was stress.

28:37.047 --> 28:38.048
Didn't think much of it.

28:41.751 --> 28:43.954
But after a while they became
more intense, more painful.

28:48.226 --> 28:53.598
And lately, I started
to hear sounds.

28:56.601 --> 28:58.437
What kind of sounds?

28:59.536 --> 29:01.539
They're not sounds
that I can identify.

29:02.507 --> 29:05.109
They're not voices either.

29:05.142 --> 29:06.010
They're sounds that
I've never heard before.

29:10.046 --> 29:11.048
I want to show you something.

29:17.153 --> 29:21.659
A couple of days ago somebody
left this in my house.

29:21.691 --> 29:22.594
I don't know how or why.

29:38.174 --> 29:40.844
Do you know what this is?

29:40.878 --> 29:41.880
It's an Egyptian cross.

29:47.785 --> 29:49.586
It's called Ankh.

29:49.620 --> 29:53.725
It represents the key
to hidden mysteries,

29:53.757 --> 29:57.528
a key to the kingdom of
the dead and eternal life.

30:01.932 --> 30:04.068
I had seven dreams where I see
that across again and again.

30:05.603 --> 30:07.538
I remember each
one, seven times.

30:09.574 --> 30:11.642
Does anyone else know
about all of this?

30:11.676 --> 30:12.677
No.

30:14.578 --> 30:15.980
I saw a doctor, but I didn't
tell him I hear things.

30:26.591 --> 30:28.093
You said you found it
a couple of nights ago.

30:31.728 --> 30:34.731
It was March 13.

30:34.765 --> 30:36.200
That's right.

30:36.232 --> 30:37.101
Your birthday.

30:39.870 --> 30:41.606
You remember my birthday.

30:41.639 --> 30:43.074
I remember a lot of
people's birthdays.

30:49.246 --> 30:51.016
What's your gut
feeling telling you?

30:52.850 --> 30:54.019
What do you think is happening?

31:00.157 --> 31:02.060
If someone was telling
me something like this,

31:02.093 --> 31:03.995
I would think that person
is delusional,

31:04.929 --> 31:05.930
maybe schizophrenic.

31:08.298 --> 31:09.334
Do I think I'm crazy?

31:10.634 --> 31:11.635
No.

31:12.670 --> 31:13.337
Normal?

31:14.805 --> 31:15.739
What's normal?

31:17.674 --> 31:19.176
How can I rationally
explain this drawing

31:19.209 --> 31:20.679
that appears in my dreams.

31:22.712 --> 31:23.614
How can anyone know
what's inside my head?

31:26.417 --> 31:27.352
It's just not real.

31:30.086 --> 31:32.156
Do you know I was an
atheist when I was younger?

31:34.190 --> 31:35.192
No.

31:36.459 --> 31:38.930
I'll believe it when
I see it was my motto.

31:40.965 --> 31:42.667
Basically, I didn't
believe in anything.

31:43.834 --> 31:44.835
What changed you?

31:46.170 --> 31:47.305
I became curious.

31:49.774 --> 31:53.378
Our eyes are great to read a
book or drive, watch a movie.

