01:05:40.069 --> 01:05:42.138
There was something
about those lights.

01:05:42.171 --> 01:05:45.841
It's just nuts, Father,
But I felt strange.

01:05:45.873 --> 01:05:48.743
Felt I needed to
go to your house.

